        id: "tk-async-loop",
        fn: "asyncio + Tk — running an async loop alongside mainloop",
        desc: "Tkinter has no native async support. The cleanest pattern: run asyncio in a worker thread, use a `queue.Queue` for thread→GUI handoff, and `asyncio.run_coroutine_threadsafe` for GUI→async. Reach for this when you have an async library (httpx, websockets, asyncpg) and a Tk UI.",
